**What each layer covers**

| Situation | What runs |
|---|---|
| stdout is not a terminal (pipe, redirect) | plain `print!` |
| Unix with `less` | `less -R` (ANSI colours preserved) |
| Unix with only `more` | `more` |
| Windows, Git-for-Windows / Scoop `less` installed | `less -R` |
| Windows, no `less` | `more.com` (always present in System32) |
| Minimal container, no pager at all | built-in line-by-line pager |
